**Loyal Cupid** | Unaligned Align | Transformation
__Basics__
The Loyal Cupid is a cupid who's lover is unable to betray their team.
__Details__
The Loyal Cupid is similar in every way to the cupid except for one detail, the Loyal Cupid is immune to role and alignment changes.
The Loyal Cupid is created when their lover is either a devout villager or alpha wolf.
The Loyal Cupid copys their lover's alignment like the regular cupid and will stay this alignment for the rest of the game.

__Simplified__
The Loyal Cupid is a cupid who's lover is unable to betray their team.
